(172, 1, '2019-04-03 01:51:19', '2019-04-03 01:51:19', '<h2>lOVE WHAT YOU DO</h2>\nCreate a website and start your business so you can do what you really do.\n\n<a href=\"/about\" role=\"button\">\njoin the next tour\n</a>\n<h3>Try it Yourself</h3>\nWhat makes design&nbsp;so alluring? We&nbsp;believes the answer is designers. That\'s why we have made&nbsp;our entire focus on you - the designer. Your style, your ideas, your creativity.&nbsp;Go on -&nbsp;Try, share and design now!\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nGet Started\n</a>\n<img width=\"776\" height=\"650\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/wordpress-101/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ma.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1/wordpress-101/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ma.png 776w, http://127.0.0.1/wordpress-101/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ma-300x251.png 300w, http://127.0.0.1/wordpress-101/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ma-768x643.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 776px) 100vw, 776px\">\n\nIf you feel lost, disappointed, hesitant, or weak, return to yourself, to who you are, here and now and when you get there, you will discover yourself, like a lotus flower in full bloom, even in a muddy pond, beautiful and strong.\n<h4> Masaru Emoto</h4>\n<h3>Hello.</h3>\nI love you, won\'t you tell me your name? These immortal words by legendary musician Jim Morrison are still as relevant today, in this digital age, as they were back then.&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nLet\'s Meet\n</a>\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XHOmBV4js_E\n<h3>WordPress, made simple.</h3>\nEveryone can write, but not everyone is a writer. What makes the difference is the keen eye for detail and beauty.\n<a href=\"/about\" role=\"button\">\njoin the next tour\n</a>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-03 01:51:19', '2019-04-03 01:51:19', '', 10, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress-101/2019/04/03/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
